# Correlation Tests

## Hypothesis Tests

* null hypothesis: correlation is zero
* alternative hypothesis: we may have some evidence of a linear relationship

$$\begin{array}{rrcl}
H_{0}: & r & = & 0 \\
H_{a}: & r & \neq & 0 \\
\end{array}$$


## Not Significant


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
cor(heart_df$creatinine_phosphokinase,
    heart_df$serum_sodium,
    use = "pairwise.complete.obs")
```

